threads.title: 820-00045 power cycle
threads.message:
MacBook came in with broken screen and no turn on. No visible liquid damage.

Following all go high for 140ms @ correct voltages

All S0 rails
3v3 S4
PM_SLP_S5_L
PM_PCH_PWROK

Have tested far more than this and they check out OK. Need a break from this board so will test again later if needed / requested.

No idea where to go from here

threads.title: 820-00045 power cycle
threads.message: Probably ripped traces because it was dropped. Nothing to fix about that.
